Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:04.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,我的生活很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.93,0:00:09.87,Default2,,0,0,0,,在什麼都不知道的老公面前\N被老公的弟弟侵犯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:46.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.11,0:00:48.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.65,0:00:52.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,會生病哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.98,0:00:56.18,Default2,,0,0,0,,但是我得做完工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.05,0:00:59.39,Default2,,0,0,0,,別太勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.21,0:01:20.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.28,0:01:28.48,Default2,,0,0,0,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:28.67,Default2,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.29,0:03:49.22,Default2,,0,0,0,,抱歉 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:53.03,Default2,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:57.83,Default2,,0,0,0,,我現在身心狀態很差\N沒心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:01.77,Default2,,0,0,0,,給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.44,0:04:05.51,Default2,,0,0,0,,不會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:23.86,Default2,,0,0,0,,早知道那時候就硬逼他了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:54.09,Default2,,0,0,0,,吃飽了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:57.56,Default2,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:13.44,Default2,,0,0,0,,-不接嗎? -不用!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:16.18,Default2,,0,0,0,,我很累了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:19.38,Default2,,0,0,0,,我也想休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:24.05,Default2,,0,0,0,,一天到晚一直煩我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:26.79,Default2,,0,0,0,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:29.39,Default2,,0,0,0,,我受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:41.74,Default2,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:48.34,Default2,,0,0,0,,去睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:51.15,Default2,,0,0,0,,不用洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:55.35,Default2,,0,0,0,,就這麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:11.37,Default2,,0,0,0,,打起精神 慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:31.32,Default2,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.93,0:06:39.99,Default2,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:41.40,Default2,,0,0,0,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.53,0:06:42.93,Default2,,0,0,0,,抱歉 這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.67,Default2,,0,0,0,,我聯絡不上哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:47.47,Default2,,0,0,0,,他去上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:49.47,Default2,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.60,0:06:52.14,Default2,,0,0,0,,我剛好路過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:57.95,Default2,,0,0,0,,我最近很擔心他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:01.95,Default2,,0,0,0,,他的精神面很脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:03.89,Default2,,0,0,0,,跟真由美你結婚後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:06.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,我還以為可以放心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:12.09,Default2,,0,0,0,,他的工作好像很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:15.43,Default2,,0,0,0,,陷入瓶頸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:18.63,Default2,,0,0,0,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:22.37,Default2,,0,0,0,,我們兄弟差很多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:25.44,Default2,,0,0,0,,我動不動就翹班
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:29.78,Default2,,0,0,0,,你終於笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.71,0:07:33.11,Default2,,0,0,0,,一笑感覽就變了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:35.85,Default2,,0,0,0,,是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:40.92,Default2,,0,0,0,,我該走了 哥就拜詆你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:43.72,Default2,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:47.06,Default2,,0,0,0,,有問題就告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:51.73,Default2,,0,0,0,,隨時聯絡我 晚上也行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:54.80,Default2,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.61,0:08:07.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,今天你弟來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.28,0:08:13.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,他說很擔心你 打給他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:20.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,不需要他擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.03,0:08:25.23,Default2,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:46.12,Default2,,0,0,0,,我們明天去看電影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.48,0:09:18.89,Default2,,0,0,0,,-請喝 -謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:30.30,Default2,,0,0,0,,好久沒有一起喝酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:40.44,Default2,,0,0,0,,是幾年前的事啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:47.72,Default2,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:50.79,Default2,,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:52.79,Default2,,0,0,0,,以前也這樣過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:54.52,Default2,,0,0,0,,他考大學落榜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:58.39,Default2,,0,0,0,,之後就直在房間睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:02.60,Default2,,0,0,0,,可是有一天突然好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:07.07,Default2,,0,0,0,,就走出房間間媽 早餐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:12.01,Default2,,0,0,0,,真像他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.94,0:10:18.08,Default2,,0,0,0,,真由美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:21.15,Default2,,0,0,0,,不用想太多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:26.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,照老樣子對他就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:29.82,Default2,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:34.83,Default2,,0,0,0,,-來 -謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:46.17,Default2,,0,0,0,,今天謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.57,0:10:48.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,我才謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:53.05,Default2,,0,0,0,,這麼晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.31,0:10:55.85,Default2,,0,0,0,,有車嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:10:59.52,Default2,,0,0,0,,沒車了 我去住網咖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:03.59,Default2,,0,0,0,,住我們家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:15.60,Default2,,0,0,0,,老公最近都睡沙發\N你睡這吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.48,0:11:26.61,Default2,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.01,0:11:30.08,Default2,,0,0,0,,我在婚禮上看到你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:33.95,Default2,,0,0,0,,就愛上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.43,0:11:44.03,Default2,,0,0,0,,我知道不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.03,0:11:46.77,Default2,,0,0,0,,但我忍不住
