Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.83,0:24:04.70,Default2,,0,0,0,,-住手 -好緊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.57,0:24:08.71,Default2,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.18,0:24:15.58,Default2,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.87,0:24:42.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.37,0:25:15.91,Default2,,0,0,0,,怎啦?不吃嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.40,0:25:44.07,Default2,,0,0,0,,是的 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.27,0:25:49.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,我老公身體還是很不好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.21,0:25:53.95,Default2,,0,0,0,,請讓他休假
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.02,0:25:59.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.43,0:26:08.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.24,0:26:17.84,Default2,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.58,0:26:27.98,Default2,,0,0,0,,這是?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.58,0:26:30.38,Default2,,0,0,0,,20萬
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.98,0:26:35.19,Default2,,0,0,0,,我只能拿出這麼多了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.26,0:26:37.66,Default2,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.86,0:26:40.46,Default2,,0,0,0,,我不能收
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.13,0:26:45.07,Default2,,0,0,0,,不只大哥的事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.33,0:26:48.74,Default2,,0,0,0,,還有之前
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.14,0:26:54.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,就當是賠償
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.61,0:27:02.55,Default2,,0,0,0,,少瞧不起我
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.88,0:27:04.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,說什麼賠償
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.69,0:27:12.43,Default2,,0,0,0,,我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.42,0:28:19.89,Default2,,0,0,0,,今天這很便宜就買了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.36,0:28:22.43,Default2,,0,0,0,,你愛吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.05,0:28:45.12,Default2,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.65,0:28:48.92,Default2,,0,0,0,,被和宏侵犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.99,0:28:54.66,Default2,,0,0,0,,沒意見嗎?
