Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.00,0:30:11.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,上次很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.54,0:30:13.67,Default2,,0,0,0,,我多嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.07,0:30:16.34,Default2,,0,0,0,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.61,0:30:22.82,Default2,,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.69,0:30:27.42,Default2,,0,0,0,,不是那種意思
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.02,0:30:30.69,Default2,,0,0,0,,是想幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.56,0:30:36.63,Default2,,0,0,0,,我們是家人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.10,0:30:39.30,Default2,,0,0,0,,得互相幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.04,0:30:43.84,Default2,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.77,0:30:48.17,Default2,,0,0,0,,真由美 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.31,0:30:51.91,Default2,,0,0,0,,做了那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.58,0:30:58.32,Default2,,0,0,0,,真由美
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.05,0:31:01.86,Default2,,0,0,0,,你太漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.12,0:31:07.39,Default2,,0,0,0,,夠了 放開
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.53,0:31:12.40,Default2,,0,0,0,,我知道你愛大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.47,0:31:16.40,Default2,,0,0,0,,當我是代替品也好
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.34,0:31:20.67,Default2,,0,0,0,,在大哥恢復前
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.81,0:31:22.34,Default2,,0,0,0,,用我代替吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.28,0:31:25.68,Default2,,0,0,0,,你說什麼蠢話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.28,0:31:32.42,Default2,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.38,0:32:04.32,Default2,,0,0,0,,你其實
